  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Busy day meeting with European ministers.

In <span class="twitter-hashflag-container"><a href="/hashtag/Denmark?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Denmark</b></a><a href="/hashtag/Denmark?src=hash" dir="ltr"><img class="twitter-hashflag" src="https://abs.twimg.com/hashflags/wp2016_DEN/wp2016_DEN.png" draggable="false" alt="" /></a></span> I met Foreign Minister Anders Samuelsen.

Then on to <span class="twitter-hashflag-container"><a href="/hashtag/CzechRepublic?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>CzechRepublic</b></a><a href="/hashtag/CzechRepublic?src=hash" dir="ltr"><img class="twitter-hashflag" src="https://abs.twimg.com/hashflags/wp2016_CZE/wp2016_CZE.png" draggable="false" alt="" /></a></span> where I saw FM <a href="/stropnickym" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="3028101299"><s>@</s><b>stropnickym</b></a> and PM <a href="/AndrejBabis" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="713035525"><s>@</s><b>AndrejBabis</b></a> to discuss the strong security partnership between our countries.<a href="https://t.co/10jPYvXZwU" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/10jPYvXZwU</a></p>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Productive meetings in <span class="twitter-hashflag-container"><a href="/hashtag/Croatia?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Croatia</b></a><a href="/hashtag/Croatia?src=hash" dir="ltr"><img class="twitter-hashflag" src="https://abs.twimg.com/hashflags/wp2016_CRO/wp2016_CRO.png" draggable="false" alt="" /></a></span> today discussing our relationship after the <a href="/hashtag/UK?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>UK</b></a> leaves the <a href="/hashtag/EU?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>EU</b></a>.<a href="https://t.co/udZOixahD9" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/DExEUgov/status/970710236674904064" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/DExEUgov/status/970710236674904064"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/DExEUgov/statu</span><span class="invisible">s/970710236674904064</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">David Davis added,</p>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">David Davis Retweeted Exiting the EU Dept</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">A packed schedule today as I met with FM Katragoulas in Greece, and then Foreign Minister Szijjrt in Hungary for talks about our future relations beyond our EU exit.<a href="https://t.co/cYj7yfzleV" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/DExEUgov/status/966357615792934912" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/DExEUgov/status/966357615792934912"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/DExEUgov/statu</span><span class="invisible">s/966357615792934912</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">David Davis added,</p>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">David Davis Retweeted Exiting the EU Dept</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Reiterated the UK's absolute commitment to upholding the rights of Spanish citizens living in the UK, and vice versa, during latest constructive meeting with <a href="/AlfonsoDastisQ" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="800727059546849280"><s>@</s><b>AlfonsoDastisQ</b></a><a href="https://t.co/lQVaqDOKzd" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/DExEUgov/status/965628729019060224" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/DExEUgov/status/965628729019060224"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/DExEUgov/statu</span><span class="invisible">s/965628729019060224</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">David Davis added,</p>
  
      <div class="QuoteTweet&#10;    &#10;    &#10;    u-block js-tweet-details-fixer">
  <div class="QuoteTweet-container">
    <a class="QuoteTweet-link js-nav" href="/DExEUgov/status/965628729019060224" data-conversation-id="965628729019060224" aria-hidden="true">
    </a>

          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">Secretary of State, <span class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="2797521996"><s>@</s><b>DavidDavisMP</b></span> is traveling in <span data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Europe</b></span> this week.

        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

Cutting the $1billion funding from IS oil sales</p>

  </div>
